show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/Kq8NYu
show.description:
Aarav Kapoor thought walking away from his simple, quiet wife was the right move. Years later, he’s shocked when Riddhima Sen returns—not as a housewife, but as a successful chef and confident woman.

Now, both must work together on the same hotel project.
The twist? She’s changed. She’s powerful. And she doesn’t need him anymore.

Can Aarav fix his biggest mistake? Or has Riddhima already moved on?

Pyaar Ka Second Round is a story of love, regret, and second chances—with ego, emotions, and old memories standing in the way.
